<a href="http://www.wto.org/english/news_e/sppl_e/sppl173_e.htm" target="_self">http://www.wto.org/english/news_e/sppl_e/sppl173_e.htm</a></p><p>ICTSD, ‘Doha accord would help WTO contribute to MDGs, says Lamy’, report on Lamy’s speech to UN Millennium Development Goals Summit, <i>Bridges Weekly Trade News Digest</i>, Vol. 14, No. 32, 22 September 2010</p><p>
